rows.label: qst202209_msg0001
rows.name: Um, do you have a minute?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm looking for a boy I shocked
before...[ML:Dash ] Do you know anything?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, so you're the rumored
Shocky-Shocky Blade?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0006
rows.name:
Yeah. The story is you catch bad
kids and punish them with shocks.

rows.label: qst202209_msg0007
rows.name:
I'm not a bad kid, so you
won't shock me, right?

rows.label: qst202209_msg0009
rows.name:
Wha? Uh, yeah! I wouldn't do
something like that! Don't worry!!

rows.label: qst202209_msg0010
rows.name: Anyway, about the boy I shocked...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202209_msg0011
rows.name:
Hmmm...[ML:Dash ] I only heard the
grown-ups talking about it,
so I don't know who he is.
